  "title": "supervisor",
  "description": "<p>Admin support supervisor engineering assistant</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan and schedule works on electrical defects and maintenance</li>\n  <li>Plan for manpower deployment for works assigned</li>\n  <li>Supervise and perform maintenance of marine electrical system/component in workshops and onboard vessels.</li>\n  <li>Perform electrical wiring, cabling and modification of electrical circuit.</li>\n  <li>Test electrical systems and continuity of circuits in electrical wiring, equipment and fixtures, using testing devices such as Multimeter, Insulation tester and Process calibrator</li>\n  <li>Participate in the repair of electrical components in workshop and onboard ships.</li>\n</ul>",
